snippet.title: Cooking Princess - F3 2022 - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a mod I made for the Paper Mario Modding Jam 2022.
The mod is heavily influenced by Overcooked.

This trailer was showcased at Kaze's F3 stream.

This is a post-jam version that adds a lot of fixes, improvements, rebalances, 2 new levels, and compatibility for all emulators plus console/everdrive.

If you want to know more about this mod and where to download it you can check the itch.io page:
https://eldexter.itch.io/cooking-princess

Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/eldexter
